Requirements:
    o php 5.0 or later
    o MySQL 4.1 or later
    o Apache web server 1.3 or later
    o latest php5-gd libs
    o latest php5-gettext libs for localization

Demo:

        http://www.samanathetha.lk/capitus/

Download:
    
    o Download the latest Sahana release in your preferred format from,
        
        http://github.com/sambro
        
        
Install:

    Please see the INSTALL file.

Support:

    CAPITUS is developed through a distributed development environment. Therefore, e-mail is the preferred way 
    to discuss various items. Most of the conversations regarding the development of CAPITUS is managed through 
    the "info [at] capitus [dot] com" mailinglist.

    For those who want more general discussion on Humanitarian ICT,

        http://groups.yahoo.com/group/humanitarian-ict/

        #sahana on freenode

Other:

    CAPITUS specification,

        http://www.reliefsource.org/foss/index.php/Sahana

    CAPITUS Development Wiki for Users and Developers,

        http://www.capitus.com/wiki/


Enjoy!!!

    CAPITUS Administration

